@NODE Informations "sOME INfOS aBOUT tHE wORLD wE LIVE iN..."
@PREV Sux
@NEXT Main

@{b}                   ________________________________________
@{ub}                           Hoopsie Doopsie! Infos!

Welcome  in  5th  issue of "not so famous" ascii pack called Ascii Terror.  In
this  issue I gave you above 2.0 megabytes of ascii experiences...  I hope you
will like most of them.  I have also hope that you enjoyed previous edition of
Ascii Terror, in other way contact me and tell about your imagination of Ascii
Terror pack.


And if you don't know why this pack is published a small note...

Ascii  art  grows  day by day and if you want to be "on time" in ascii art you
should  view  all  new  ascii  collections.   Now you may cut logos from these
collections  and use in your BBS, demo, magazine or letters.  The Ascii Terror
pack is also low-quality collection filter.  In Ascii Terror is only place for
good  ascii  artist  and good logos.  (if you're an ascii artist and I haven't
published your collection please contact me or send some message!)
    
                                    * * *

As almost in every issue I again released some new collections...  Enjoy them,
because  they  really  rule!   =)  This  time  "Wicked  Sensation" and "Online
Experience".   I  hope  you'll  like them.  (if yes, try to request some logos
from me!!!)

Ok that's all I had to say... And if you wanna contact me...

@{b}
==============================================================================@{ub}
@{fg highlight}                         pASZCZAk of oBS^aZK!^vMF^cOR@{fg text}
                             ul.Hermanowska 91/1
                                54-314 WROCLAW
                                POLAND, EUROPE
@{b}==============================================================================@{ub}

               Please  put  note  about the Ascii Terror pack.
                  What changes could be done or whatever...


                          You can also reach me at:

   RUSSIA         +48-71-576946       28k8 ^ 24h        sPOONMAN/COR^ILS^OBS
