   DROP ZONE      +48-728-41652       28k8 ^ 22-8       nORBY/nAH-kOLOR/tRSI


        or simply try to send a message to following e-mail addresses:

                         2:482/22.3@fidonet    - FidoNet
                        39:200/108.3@amiganet  - AmigaNet

                     (my real name is Marcin Paszkiewicz)


Thanks alot! :-)


               yours...

                    Paszczak of Obsession ^ Azkiness ^ Virtual MF ^ Corrupt
